-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Illustrator drawing --> Processing code

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Florian Jenett, 2008 - 2010
	http://bezier.de/processing/ai2p/

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Instructions:
	
	- draw something in Illustrator
	
	- save your drawing somewhere
	
	- run menu command
	  File > Scripts > Other Scripts ...
	  
	- choose "AiCS2toProsessing.js"
	
	[ .. script is running .. ]
	
	- now there should be a ".pde" next to your ".ai"
	
	- open the ".pde" in Processing and see if it worked

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------